# Formal Data / 正式数据

This directory contains only validated, user-approved, publication-ready artifacts.

## Rules

- Preserve source data in `raw_data`.
- Reproduce artifacts with code in `code` before promotion.
- Preview promotion with `promote_formal_data.py --dry-run`.
- Require explicit user approval before `--approve`.
- Never overwrite an existing artifact.
- Record every artifact in `MANIFEST.csv`.
